des: KPDO, 89.3 FM Pescadero/San Gregorio, is the voice of San Mateo County and the South Coast. KPDO provides Community Programming in English and Spanish. Local events and news, road conditions and closures, community meetings and school closings all right here on KPDO 89.3 FM. Enjoy new local music and programming. KPDO is operated by Pescadero Public Radio.
